name: Harem dancer
description:
This LoRA can generate Harem outfit, Dancer, as well as face veil (mouth veil) and see-through clothes.

The training data for harem outfits are more revealing, while dancers are more gorgeous, but the actually generated results may vary.

To generate face veil, both Face veil and Mouth veil can be used, both are effective and can be switched depending on the situation.

Due to the training results of the LoRA, almost anything that is wrapped around the mouth will become transparent, so prompts such as mask may also be affected, maybe they can help generate face veils.

There may be some issues when generating head veil probably because its keyword has been taken.

Face veils are the main focus of this LoRA, but it is more difficult than expected, and there are still many problems with the generating.

If needed, this LoRA can also be used on male characters.

Note: standing_on_one_leg can solve some anatomical issues when dancing.
Useful prompts: ornate, intricate, water, light particles, glitters, shiny, belly chain, anklet, dress, wind
